OL,3,CCambridge-educated doctor avoids jail
OL,4,Ctime after filming men in urinals
OL,6,FA Cambridge-educated doctor who was
OL,7,Ftraining at Jersey Hospital has
OL,8,Favoided prison after filming multiple
OL,9,Fmen urinating in toilets across the
OL,10,Fisland, but will be put on the sex
OL,11,Foffenders register for at least five
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,F27-year-old Diego Balassini,
OL,15,Foriginally from Tuscany, appeared in
OL,16,FJersey's Royal Court on Friday 23
OL,17,FJanuary, convicted of nine counts of
OL,18,Fvoyeurism.
