OL,3,CCambridge-educated doctor avoids jail
OL,4,Ctime after filming men in urinals
OL,6,FThe counts include filming men
OL,7,Furinating in public bathrooms inside a
OL,8,Fpub and a bar, but also at Jersey's
OL,9,FAirport.
OL,11,FBalassini was caught after a man
OL,12,Fspotted him filming him naked at a
OL,13,Fgym, and the States of Jersey Police
OL,14,Fwere called. Officers then found other
OL,15,Fvideos on his phone from across the
OL,16,Fisland.
OL,18,FPolice also found multiple devices at
OL,19,Fhis home, as well as a hard drive.
