OL,6,FCommissioner Sir William Bailache, the
OL,7,Fpresiding judge, told the court during
OL,8,Fsentencing that the hard drive showed
OL,9,Ffurther evidence of a fascination with
OL,10,Furination and covert filming.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, Balassini said in
OL,13,Fcourt that he didn't take the videos
OL,14,Ffor sexual gratification but in a
OL,15,F"dissociative state", and added that
OL,16,Fhe felt compelled to take and keep the
OL,17,Fvideos to make him feel "shame and
OL,18,Fdisgust".
