OL,6,FHowever, the court disagreed, and his
OL,7,Fdefence argued he had complex mental
OL,8,Fhealth issues.
OL,10,FOne of Balassini's victims said the
OL,11,Fincident had had a destructive effect
OL,12,Fon them and left them feeling isolated
OL,13,Fand depressed.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Health and Care Jersey
OL,16,Ftold ITV News: "We are aware that a
OL,17,Fformer employee of HCJ has been on
OL,18,Ftrial for acts perpetrated outside of
OL,19,Ftheir place of employment.
