OL,6,F"We have no further comment on their
OL,7,Fcase."
OL,9,FBalassini has now been put on the sex
OL,10,Foffenders register for at least five
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FHe will be monitored by probation for
OL,14,Ftwo years with conditions including
OL,15,Fnot having a phone, agreeing to
OL,16,Fmedical treatment, and providing his
OL,17,Faddress before he returns to the UK.
OL,19,FIt is up to the General Medical
OL,20,FCouncil to determine if Balassini is
OL,21,Ffit to practice again.
